          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Improving Broadband Access for Veterans Act of 2017</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Federal Communications Commission (FCC) to submit to Congress a report on promoting broadband Internet access service for veterans, in particular low-income veterans and veterans residing in rural areas. </p> <p> In preparing the report, the FCC shall provide the public with notice and an opportunity to comment.</p>]]></text>
